<font color="#FF0000">M24 GOT RUN OVER BY A REINDEER</font><br>
<tt>Sun Dec 14 10:53:50 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
M24 GOT RUN OVER BY A REINDEER<br><br>
M Two Four got run over by a reindeer<br>
Flying home from the PX Christmas eve.<br>
You can say there's no such thing as Santa,<br>
But as for me and PePe, we believe.<br><br>
M24 had been drinkin' too much egg nog,<br>
And we'd begged him not to go.<br>
But he said he left his metamucil in his chopper,<br>
So he stumbled out the door into the snow.<br><br>
When they found him Christmas mornin',<br>
At the scene of the attack.<br>
There were hoof prints on his forehead,<br>
And incriminatin' Claus marks on his back.<br><br>
M24 got run over by a reindeer<br>
Flying home his chooper Christmas eve.<br>
You can say there's no such thing as Santa,<br>
But as for me and BoBo, we believe.<br><br>
Now they’ve molded up a new medal,<br>
One that’s honor him for takin' this so well.<br>
Santa saw him flying barefoot and backwards,<br>
And stopped his reindeer to see what was that smell.<br><br>
It seemed this Christmas would be different<br>
So M24 went out to catch Santa in his tracks <br>
He had super charged his chopper .<br>
But didn’t count on reindeers at his back<br><br>
M24 got run over by a reindeer<br>
Trying to catch Santa Christmas eve.<br>
You can say there's no such thing as Santa,<br>
But as for me and Art, we believe.<br><br>
Now all the reindeer, Santa and Ed are in the hospital<br>
Celebrating Christmas in the dark.<br>
Their fight was so terrific,<br>
It knocked out all the electricity on the block<br><br>
We've warned all our friends and neighbours.<br>
&quot;Better watch out for yourselves.&quot;<br>
Foe Ed last night captured Santa , <br>
Just to see a man who drives a sleigh and plays with elves.<br><br>
M24 got run over by a reindeer<br>
Fighting with them Christmas eve.<br>
You can say there's no such thing as Santa,<br>
But as for me and Gary, we believe.<br><br>
Merry christmas to all and to all a Good Night!<br><br>
Sparrowhawk<br><br>

